CHANGELOG
=========

VERSION 0.0.3 (2026-01-22)
--------------------------

Added:
- `misty-parser`: Validator module Workspace struct.
- `misty-parser`: Full workspace validator implementation.

Changed:
- `misty-parser`: Added crate scoping to the public uses of the AST parsers.
- `misty-core`: Bumped to 0.0.2.
- `misty-parser`: Bumped to 0.0.3.

VERSION 0.0.2 (2026-01-22)
--------------------------

Added:
- `misty-ast`: File AST node.
- `misty-ast`: Full AST definition for the Misty language.
- `misty-core`: Basic error shells.
- `misty-parser`: Pest parser and grammar for Misty.
- `misty-parser`: All AST node parsers.

Changed:
- `misty-core`: Refactored to remove errors for improved flexibility.
- `misty-ast`: Bumped to 0.0.2.
- `misty-parser`: Bumped to 0.0.2.

VERSION 0.0.1 (2026-01-21)
--------------------------

Added:
- Initial workspace scaffolding and crate layout.